body:
things i’m working on

i’m a pretty avid marvel fan, and i have a few projects i’m working on right now, if anyone is interested. i’m gonna post them here as soon as they’re done (or at least make a bit of sense). i take requests, and i’m up for almost anything since i’m a kinky bitch with a taste for angst.

🌟 marvel headcanons: hogwarts au 🌟

yeah i know everyone has done it before, but i don’t really care, i just like to write them out and imagine everything

🌟 ironstrange fic 🌟

this one is coming along well, i might have the first chapter soon, but it’ll talk about triggering topics such as anxiety, ptsd, suicide, depression, and other mental-health issues. there will be a lot of fluff and maybe some smut

🌟 frostiron oneshots 🌟

i just have the need to pair these two together and make them have kinky sex. needless to say, it’ll be rated E

🌟 winteriron fic(let?) 🌟

you probably figured out by now i love tony and ship him with everyone. i actually have very little for this one, and i’m accepting ideas if you have any

🌟 thorbruce (thruce is too weird for me sorry) drabbles 🌟

i love this pairing and need more of them in my life. it’ll be mainly fluff or a bit of angst with a fluffy end. i might eventually do smut too but not right now

🌟 carol x maria/ pepper/ valkyrie/ nebula/ literary every single female character 🌟

i love carol and i headcanon her as wlw so there will be a lot of this. there’ll be fics, oneshots, drabbles, aus, everything. this will most likely include smut too because the fandom (and the world in general) is lacking lesbian sex written by someone with experience in the field

🌟 carol gen ficlets 🌟

again i simply love her and want to write about her being powerful, kicking ass, taking names, and saving the avengers’ asses

ps: i’m in other fandoms too, and if you’d like to request something that isn’t marvel related you’re more than welcome
